  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the safety and efficacy for long term treatment
      of the drug in children aged 6 months and &lt; 5 years on bronchial asthma in daily clinical
      usage.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
